- Founded within the last 24 months
- Self-serve or product-led growth (no sales calls required)
- Customers can sign up and pay without human interaction&lt;p&gt;What we're offering:&lt;p&gt;- Up to $1 million per acquisition
- Our AI takes on the CEO role and operationalizes the business
- Target: ideally double revenue in the first six months&lt;p&gt;We're looking for founders who are willing to take a bet on this approach. If you're interested or know someone who is, we'd like to hear from you (submit your company here” https://skyfall.ai/acquisition ).&lt;p&gt;PS: We’re accepting submissions through August 31!&lt;/p&gt;
